{"tid":1492143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠：2022年檢討一國兩制","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T18:21:57.000Z","uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b663c320b3820af3227d585cfb54324bac96015a","tid":1492143,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:45:27.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂風波至今持續逾兩個月仍未平息，基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠日前接受傳媒查詢時指出，在下一任特首上任後，即2022年，應由全國人大常委會領頭檢討「一國兩制」，了解當中「有甚麼是香港做得不足，有甚麼是中央做得不足，香港在中國發展的地位有甚麼可以改善，扮演甚麼角色」，料需時最少兩年。她又認為中央政府和香港政府均需反思，未來應如何幫助香港人認識「一國兩制」、國家主權和管治權。 <br />\n<br />\n對於連日來不斷升溫的示威衝突，譚感到十分憂心，希望能盡快平息，但認為事件不會動搖中央政府推行「一國兩制」的信心，但有需要檢討「一國兩制」，形容國家與香港之間是「命運共同體」，直言香港不可以再拿起英國旗揮來揮去，亦不可以要求美國對香港提供充足的「糧草」。 <br />\n<br />\n譚又指，平息風波首要條件是回復法治，但不認為民間一直要求成立獨立調查委員會有助平息風波，強調過往的獨立調查委員會均是在事件完結後才開始調查，若其目標是警察，則已有監警會調查，認為不需要獨立調查委員會，認為示威者其他訴求不合理。至於社會上的各項不滿，則可循《施政報告》中處理。 <br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學專業及持續教育學院陳偉強表示，一國兩制現時已非如預期般運行良好，香港正面對危機，2022年將發展到如何都是未知數，故應以快打慢，盡快檢討一國兩制上有何不足及缺失，甚至舊有的「兩制」應否繼續。他又認為，要令暴亂情況平息不止靠出動警方平亂，治本的方法是在制度上改變，解決問題，才是明智的方法。 <br />\n<br />\n時事評論員陳雲生指，一國兩制一直存有未完善的地方，即使沒有修例風波，亦需適時檢討。"},{"pid":"b0b15455b964c7092f87b6bb29d8eb34271b25ea","tid":1492143,"uid":123111,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:46:23.000Z","msg":"距到底明唔明咩係命運共同體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2544ac657b044f6acee078aed9f313b501cc2847","tid":1492143,"uid":2562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMcAke7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMcAke7.png&h=5d1306ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee2b64a93d3b1fae2798f6772b8533367b596cb4","tid":1492143,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n股樓齊爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15cc17fdb7426248ab2861569bbfbada2a58fa9","tid":1492143,"uid":259813,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:49:31.000Z","msg":"唔使檢討啦，呢家即刻一國一制啦"},{"pid":"0f9a9052c2532f9aeff1db894af416be3f9dc91c","tid":1492143,"uid":9570,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:50:40.000Z","msg":"佢到時都係話一國一制<br />\n<br />\n出老解啦，快點制裁我"},{"pid":"9de8b7448abca7a4291254eff7ba6494a0991cfe","tid":1492143,"uid":279810,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"2022 身份證換哂新嘅, 街燈又裝哂, digital id 又推埋, 全面監控已完工, 明哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906939be3d5034337d6ce15227049ef9b720ca92","tid":1492143,"uid":13466,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠呢個妖婦，六、七年前我曾經要freelance幫手做演講逐字紀錄，抽中要去聽佢個基本法講座。<br />\n<br />\n佢講「高度自治」嗰節，睇到我呆撚咗。<br />\n佢先邀請一個高佬同一個矮妹（矮過譚）上台企佢左右兩側，然後話：「高度自治其實唔係一個絕對概念，只係相對概念。」<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢指住個高佬話：「拿，佢高過我，所以佢就係高度自治，我就係低度自治。」再指住個矮妹話：「拿，而家我高過佢，所以我又變番係高度自治，佢就係低度自治了。」<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街，喺呢班冚家剷嘅角度而言，只要香港未衰到好似當年比利時管治剛果咁切人手掌，咁已經係高度自治啦！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母。"},{"pid":"64692de8274b52efc5834ee96fdc58eb90a4ffdc","tid":1492143,"uid":61840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:11:57.000Z","msg":"cancer腫瘤呢d真真正正係命運共同體<br />\n老閪都要割 ，切走佢。<br />\n係咪暗指香港係中國既腫瘤，要切。原來潭惠珠想搞港獨，反中亂港叛國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b76ba43c6b32457e50cfe359568ab2af4ba28a0","tid":1492143,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"呢條冚家剷真係毒瘤黎<br />\n2022年社會信用體系同監控燈柱晨早起哂啦<br />\n你唔撚快D去死"},{"pid":"a257b3ad200e4f6fe9a5b145478dee423b4a72b8","tid":1492143,"uid":245484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:18:31.000Z","msg":"2022 仲有中共再講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0065c91f98f6b6e536b378b764dbfb135943efd2","tid":1492143,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:18:57.000Z","msg":"香港咁唔聽話，即刻檢討啦屌你老母仲等，正一賣國賊"},{"pid":"f4a093fe18dd790b3b2bbd78fd219033ea6b5748","tid":1492143,"uid":42379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"到時條八婆分分鐘已壽終正寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b6e71daef9c7835b9a68826cd8e041fbaf3d42","tid":1492143,"uid":76776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91f11b215b8ef47bacdf9fbf10ca9526e03efe3f","tid":1492143,"uid":249794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:20:26.000Z","msg":"到時支爆左啦 捱到咁耐先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1306aef849ba841b89cc6104cdb24885295d8eb","tid":1492143,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"4fe75083a243c0b71f104e11b7ff7f82eeeb4a53","tid":1492143,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:21:37.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠日前接受傳媒查詢時指出，在下一任特首上任後，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁講姐係明知777做唔住 都要死攬到2022先換人<br />\n你肯到佢仲頂到3年 唔會搞到香港攬炒??"},{"pid":"1aa1580823b4ddbb5bfe051e5195089808d90973","tid":1492143,"uid":36612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"到時你仲在生再講啦"},{"pid":"9f197d0c0e69304d3728863d5fa4a2da6f3987c5","tid":1492143,"uid":189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"以前係英國人隻狗，宜家係中國人隻狗，死八婆成世都係牆頭草"},{"pid":"29b4d3cdb633ea85cd8c1609b4c427d44bb2df2d","tid":1492143,"uid":37350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:22:23.000Z","msg":"幾時死呀老而不"},{"pid":"7902ab03ca4265f70bcdacb6c7a4bcff9a419bad","tid":1492143,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"立左timeline <br />\n得返三年俾唔想做中國人既搞移民<br />\n更可能係俾料外國人走"},{"pid":"170ea9ffaf6ca0bee69651d8d6c0fa4cb866dff4","tid":1492143,"uid":295262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:22:59.000Z","msg":"發覺賣港呢班全部都係閪老女人：林奠、譚惠珠、梁愛詩、范徐麗泰、葉瘤、羅范椒芬"},{"pid":"cbf736de8ef641a8fa20305f1df6edf757004981","tid":1492143,"uid":52609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"收皮啦仲2022年，今年我就要你過唔到七十大壽"},{"pid":"2a57db3e5f47d281a52a1d3714b3e6e574cb6b86","tid":1492143,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"2022 佢都死靗左啦 係咪想何妖起佢個墳呀"},{"pid":"17a8ea26e009c4b482cd4e4d3195cca3b50484b7","tid":1492143,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2022 佢都死撚左啦 係咪想何妖起佢個墳呀</blockquote>"}]}